		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>You can learn a lot of different situational Japanese if you like variety in your anime. It&#8217;s not all just the Japanese equivalent of Popeye or whatever. Eventually it becomes easy to pick up on when a character has some amusing idiosyncrasy in the way they speak-su~.</p>
